---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Trucking Insurance for New Authorities | RMS Insurance">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="new-venture-badge">
        <span class="badge-icon">&#9679;</span>
        <span>New Venture & New DOT Specialists</span>
      </div>

      <h1>Finally, trucking insurance that <span class="gold">makes sense.</span></h1>

      <p class="hero-sub">Don't just get coverage. Get explanations.</p>

      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="hero-cta">
        <span class="cta-label">Talk to an Expert</span>
        <span class="cta-number">208-800-0640</span>
      </a>

      <div class="hero-trust">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">1,000+</span>
          <span class="trust-text">Truckers Helped</span>
        </div>
        <span class="trust-sep"></span>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">$4.4M</span>
          <span class="trust-text">Premium Written</span>
        </div>
        <span class="trust-sep"></span>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <span class="trust-num">10,000+</span>
          <span class="trust-text">Hours of Expert Advice</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW AUTHORITY CALLOUT -->
  <section class="new-authority">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="na-grid">
        <div class="na-content">
          <span class="na-label">For New Authorities</span>
          <h2>Just Got Your DOT?<br/><span class="gold">We've Got You.</span></h2>
          <p>Getting insurance for a new authority is different. Most agents don't explain the process—they just send you a bill. We walk you through every coverage, every requirement, every step.</p>
          <a href="/new-authorities" class="btn-outline">Learn What You Actually Need →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY RMS -->
  <section class="why-rms">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Why RMS</span>
        <h2>The Industry Profits From Your Confusion.<br/><span class="gold">We Don't.</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="value-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>We Actually Explain Things</h3>
          <p>Insurance should make sense to you. If your agent can't explain it clearly, they either don't understand it or don't want you to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>We Know Your Business First</h3>
          <p>We ask what you haul, where you go, how you run. Then we find coverage that actually fits. Not maximum coverage. Right coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>When You Call, Things Happen</h3>
          <p>You say what you need, it happens. Certificate requests get done while you're on the phone. One moment... done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COVERAGE -->
  <section class="coverage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="section-tag">Coverage</span>
        <h2>Commercial Trucking Insurance<br/>That Actually <span class="gold">Makes Sense</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro">We specialize in commercial trucking insurance for owner-operators and small fleets. Every coverage we offer, we can explain in plain English.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="coverage-grid">
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge required">Required by FMCSA</span>
          <h3>Auto Liability</h3>
          <p>The coverage that keeps you legal. Protects you when you're at fault in an accident. Federal law requires $750,000 minimum for interstate carriers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge">Protect Your Truck</span>
          <h3>Physical Damage</h3>
          <p>Covers your rig if it's damaged or totaled—collision, fire, theft, vandalism. This is the coverage that lets you sleep at night.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge">Protect What You Haul</span>
          <h3>Cargo Insurance</h3>
          <p>Covers the freight you're hauling if it's damaged, stolen, or lost. Required by most brokers and shippers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge">Slip and Fall</span>
          <h3>General Liability</h3>
          <p>Protects your business when you're not in the truck—loading docks, customer locations, your office.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge">Off-Dispatch</span>
          <h3>Non-Trucking Liability</h3>
          <p>Covers you when you're driving but not under dispatch—heading home, running errands, bobtailing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <span class="coverage-badge">Your Safety Net</span>
          <h3>Occupational Accident</h3>
          <p>Medical coverage and disability protection if you're injured on the job. For owner-operators not covered by workers' comp.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE SERVE -->
  <section class="who-we-serve">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Who We Serve</span>
        <h2>Built for Truckers.<br/><span class="gold">Only Truckers.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-intro">We don't do home insurance. We don't do life insurance. This is all we do.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="customer-grid">
        <div class="customer-card">
          <span class="customer-type">1-3 Trucks</span>
          <h3>Owner-Operators</h3>
          <p>You own your truck. You run your business. You need an agent who understands that every dollar matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="customer-card">
          <span class="customer-type">Just Got Your MC/DOT?</span>
          <h3>New Authorities</h3>
          <p>Starting a trucking company is complicated enough. We specialize in new authorities and know exactly what you need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="customer-card">
          <span class="customer-type">3-10 Trucks</span>
          <h3>Small Fleets</h3>
          <p>Growing your fleet means growing your coverage. Same fast service, same straight answers, just bigger policies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="customer-card">
          <span class="customer-type">Hotshot • General Freight • Towing</span>
          <h3>Specific Operations</h3>
          <p>Different operations need different coverage. We match coverage to your actual business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="section-tag">Process</span>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <h4>Tell Us About Your Operation</h4>
          <p>Quick call or form. We ask the right questions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <h4>Get Options That Fit</h4>
          <p>We explain what you're actually buying.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-line"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <h4>Stay Covered, Stay Moving</h4>
          <p>Certs when you need them. Answers when you have questions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header centered">
        <span class="section-tag">Reviews</span>
        <h2>What Truckers Say</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"First agent who actually explained what I was buying instead of just sending me a bill."</p>
          <footer><strong>Marcus T.</strong> · Owner-Operator, Texas</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"Called at 7am needing a cert. Had it in my email before I finished my coffee."</p>
          <footer><strong>Jennifer R.</strong> · Small Fleet Owner, Idaho</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"New authority, didn't know what I was doing. They walked me through everything."</p>
          <footer><strong>David K.</strong> · New Authority, California</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUOTE FORM -->
  <section class="quote-section" id="quote">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="quote-layout">
        <div class="quote-info">
          <span class="section-tag">Get Started</span>
          <h2>Get a Quote</h2>
          <p>Fill out the form and we'll call you back. Usually same day.</p>
          <ul class="quote-benefits">
            <li>No obligation quote</li>
            <li>We explain everything</li>
            <li>Same day response</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="quote-alt">Or call: <a href="tel:208-800-0640">208-800-0640</a></p>
        </div>

        <form class="quote-form">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="name">Your Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="John Smith">
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="phone">Phone</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required placeholder="(555) 123-4567">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@example.com">
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="dot">DOT Number</label>
              <input type="text" id="dot" name="dot" placeholder="1234567">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="status">Where are you in the process?</label>
            <select id="status" name="status">
              <option value="">Select one...</option>
              <option value="researching">Still researching</option>
              <option value="getting-dot">Getting my DOT now</option>
              <option value="new-authority">Just got my authority</option>
              <option value="established">Established, shopping for better service</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="message">Anything else?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="What you haul, how many trucks..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Get My Quote</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-layout">
        <div class="faq-header">
          <span class="section-tag">FAQ</span>
          <h2>Straight Answers</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How much does trucking insurance cost?</summary>
            <p>It depends on experience, equipment, what you haul, and safety record. New authority with newer truck: expect $12,000-$18,000/year. We'll give you a real quote based on your situation.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Is your price lower than other agencies?</summary>
            <p>Probably not much different—we use the same carriers. The difference is who picks up when you call and whether they actually know the answer.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How fast can I get a quote?</summary>
            <p>Most quotes same day. If you have your info ready, often within a couple hours.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>I just got my authority. Where do I start?</summary>
            <p>Call us. We'll walk you through what coverage you need and how to get your filings done.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Do I need cargo insurance?</summary>
            <p>Practically yes—most brokers won't work with you without it. Standard is $100K.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-layout">
        <div class="about-content">
          <span class="section-tag">About</span>
          <h2>Why RMS Exists</h2>
          <p class="about-lead">RMS Insurance was founded on a simple frustration: truckers deserve better.</p>
          <p>Trucking insurance isn't complicated—the industry just profits from keeping you confused. We started RMS because that sticks in our craw.</p>
          <p>When you call RMS, things happen. Fast and right. You get straight answers in plain English.</p>
          <p class="about-emphasis">That's what "finally, someone on your side" means.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-facts">
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-label">Founded</span><span class="fact-value">2022</span></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-label">Location</span><span class="fact-value">Idaho (serving nationwide)</span></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-label">Founder</span><span class="fact-value">Jake Deaton, former trial attorney</span></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-label">Focus</span><span class="fact-value">Commercial trucking only</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="cta-label">Ready to talk?</p>
      <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="cta-phone">208-800-0640</a>
      <p class="cta-sub">We answer.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MOBILE STICKY -->
  <div class="mobile-cta">
    <a href="tel:208-800-0640" class="mobile-btn">Call for Quote</a>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ========================================
     VARIABLES & BASE
     ======================================== */
  :root {
    --forest: #1B4332;
    --forest-deep: #0D2118;
    --gold: #DAA520;
    --gold-hover: #B8860B;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --gray-100: #f7f7f7;
    --gray-200: #e5e5e5;
    --gray-600: #6b7280;
    --text: #1f2937;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .gold { color: var(--gold); }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header.centered {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ========================================
     HERO - Clean, minimal, conversion-focused
     ======================================== */
  .hero {
    min-height: auto;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--forest-deep);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .new-venture-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: rgba(218,165,32,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(218,165,32,0.3);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .badge-icon {
    font-size: 6px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--forest-deep);
    padding: 1.25rem 3.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .cta-number {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .trust-num {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .trust-text {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .trust-sep {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* ========================================
     NEW AUTHORITY
     ======================================== */
  .new-authority {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #E8D5A3;
  }

  .na-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--forest);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .new-authority h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .new-authority p {
    color: var(--forest);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border: 2px solid var(--forest);
    color: var(--forest);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--forest);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ========================================
     WHY RMS
     ======================================== */
  .why-rms {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--forest-deep);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .why-rms .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ========================================
     COVERAGE
     ======================================== */
  .coverage {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .coverage .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--forest);
  }

  .coverage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coverage-card {
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }

  .coverage-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--forest);
    background: rgba(27,67,50,0.1);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .coverage-badge.required {
    background: rgba(218,165,32,0.2);
    color: var(--gold-hover);
  }

  .coverage-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .coverage-card p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ========================================
     WHO WE SERVE
     ======================================== */
  .who-we-serve {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--forest);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .who-we-serve .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .who-we-serve .section-intro {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  .customer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .customer-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .customer-type {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .customer-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .customer-card p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ========================================
     HOW IT WORKS
     ======================================== */
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }

  .how-it-works .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--forest);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 250px;
  }

  .step-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-200);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step h4 {
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .step-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gray-200);
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ========================================
     TESTIMONIALS
     ======================================== */
  .testimonials {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--white);
